quran[10{c,v,t}:
25,68,"jo Allah ke siwa kisi aur mabood ko nahi pukarte, Allah ki haraam ki hui kisi jaan ko na-haq halaak nahi karte, aur nah zina ke murtakib hotay hain yeh kaam jo koi kere woh apne gunah ka badla paye ga"
25,69,qayamat ke roz is ko mkrrr azaab diya jaye ga aur isi mein woh hamesha zillat ke sath para rahay ga
25,70,ila yeh ke koi ( un gunaaho ke baad ) tauba kar chuka ho aur imaan laa kar amal Saleh karne laga ho aisay logon ki buraiyon ko Allah bhulaiyon se badal day ga aur woh bara ghafoor Raheem hai
25,71,jo shakhs tauba kar ke naik amli ikhtiyar karta hai woh to Allah ki taraf palat aata hai jaissa ke palatnay ka haq hai
25,72,( aur rehman ke bande woh hain ) jo jhoot ke gawah nahi bantay aur kisi laghu cheez par un ka guzar ho jaye to shareef admion ki terhan guzar jatay hain
25,73,jinhein agar unn ke rab ki ayaat suna kar nasiyaat ki jati hai to woh is par andhay aur behray ban kar nahi reh jatay
25,74,"jo duayen manga karte hain ke"" ae hamaray rab, hamein apni biwion aur apni aulaad se aankhon ki thandak day aur hum ko parhaiz gaaron ka imam bana """
25,75,yeh hain woh log jo apne sabr ka phal manzil buland ki shakal mein payen ge aadaab o tasleemaat se unn ka istaqbaal ho ga
25,76,woh hamesha hamesha wahan rahen ge kya hi acha hai woh mstqr aur woh maqam
25,77,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, logon se kaho"" mere rab ko tumhari kya haajat pari hai agar tum is ko nah poukaro ab ke tum ne jhutla diya hai, anqareeb woh saza pao ge ke jaan chhrhani mahaal ho gi """
